if add new files:
git add .

a flag for common file:
git commit -a -m "Improve the README file"
git log
git status

 TO revert changes:
git checkout -f

Change to branch:
git checkout -b modify-README
git branch

Merge back to master copy:
gic checkout master
git merge modify-README

Tidy up branch:
git branch -d modify-README
      
full steps:

  mkdir first_app
  cd first_app
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:wmliew88/first_app.git
  git push -u origin master